entry.title: Prime Minister Netanyahu suspended a controversial judicial-overhaul plan in a bid to pull Israel back from the brink after mass protests and strikes rocked the nation.

entry.title: Explosions shook Russian-occupied cities in southern Ukraine, while a Russian missile strike killed at least two people and injured 29 in the eastern city of Slovyansk, Ukrainian officials said.
entry.content: Explosions shook Russian-occupied cities in southern Ukraine, while a Russian missile strike killed at least two people and injured 29 in the eastern city of Slovyansk, Ukrainian officials said.
